                             ENGLISH

Cross Country had 2 separate archives called: CrossCountry and Cross Disk
2.   Cross Country is the name of the disk 1 and Cross Disk 2 the name of
the disk 2.

The  installer  script  is  only  usefull  if you want to install the game
directly with the 2 disks.  Installer is included in the disk 1.

But It's possible to install directly the game by creating a drawer called
CrossCountry  and manually copy all the files.  Assigning Cross Country is
necessary to use the game.

Cross  Country  is  a very good game programmed in Amos.  We have meet the
author  at the AmigaShow98 (Bruxelles) and we are allright to put his game
to Aminet.  Don't hesitate to contact the author and/or send him a gift to
encourage him !!!!

Uploader E-Mail: Philippe Bovier ( *Mrod* )

<9K: Philippe.Bovier@ramses.fdn.org
